mso-bidi-font-family:NimbusSanL-Regu;mso-font-kerning:0pt&quot;&gt;Notwithstanding the
Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) Order 2015 (or any
Order revoking, re-enacting or modifying that Order), any part of the hereby
approved development shall not be permitted for waste or recycling services.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

